OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1772460675
OL,3,CTfL announces further delays to new
OL,4,Cfleet of Piccadilly Line trains
OL,6,FTransport for London has announced a
OL,7,F#400m delay to the arrival of its new
OL,8,FPiccadilly Line trains.
OL,10,FThe fleet of 94 air-conditioned trains
OL,11,Fwas due to enter service last year but
OL,12,Fwas postponed until the end of this
OL,13,Fyear.
OL,15,FNow further software issues mean the
OL,16,Ffirst train might not enter service
OL,17,Funtil summer 2027.
OL,19,FTfL has admitted the delay will be
OL,20,F"hugely disappointing" for customers.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
