PN,40802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1772460675
OL,3,CTfL announces further delays to new
OL,4,Cfleet of Piccadilly Line trains
OL,6,FChief Capital Officer Stuart Harvey
OL,7,Fsaid: "The programme of work that we
OL,8,Fare undertaking to bring these game-
OL,9,Fchanging trains to London is hugely
OL,10,Fcomplex and is underpinned by our
OL,11,Fsteadfast commitment to safety.
OL,13,F"It is critical that we do everything
OL,14,Fwe can to make sure that, when they
OL,15,Fenter service, we are confident that
OL,16,Fthese trains are ready to operate
OL,17,Fsafely.
OL,26,@oD@GOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1772460675
OL,3,CTfL announces further delays to new
OL,4,Cfleet of Piccadilly Line trains
OL,6,F"Despite this change in delivery
OL,7,Fschedule, our teams have been working
OL,8,Fintensely to push the programme
OL,9,Fforward."
OL,11,FAccording to TfL, each new train
OL,12,Fprovides 10 per cent more capacity and
OL,13,Fconsume 20 per cent less energy.
OL,15,FThe network has also announced that it
OL,16,Fis seeking to increase the budget for
OL,17,Fthe update by #409m to #3.4bn.
OL,19,FThe Piccadilly Line is currently
OL,20,Fserved by trains from the early 1970s.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
