OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1772460675
OL,3,CTfL announces further delays to new
OL,4,Cfleet of Piccadilly Line trains
OL,6,FThe new fleet feature walk-through
OL,7,Fcarriages, wider double doorways, real-
OL,8,Ftime digital displays and on-board
OL,9,FCCTV.
OL,11,FIt said it has worked to "minimise"
OL,12,Fthe additional costs and will continue
OL,13,Fto look for savings.
OL,15,FCommuters told ITV News London the
OL,16,Fline was in desperate need of an
OL,17,Fupgrade.
OL,19,F"It is bad, it is one of the worst
OL,20,Flines around. We need new trains," one
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
