PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1772460675
OL,3,CTfL announces further delays to new
OL,4,Cfleet of Piccadilly Line trains
OL,6,FAnother agreed, but said she didn't
OL,7,Fmind waiting: "I want them to come out
OL,8,Fwith proper trains rather than being
OL,9,Fhalf done or whatnot."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/5
